quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  40,66,"Yithi (Muhammad): “Inene mna ndalelwa ukuba ndinqule abo nibanqulayo ngaphandle koAllâh, nje ukufika kwemiqondiso evela eNkosini yam, kwaye mna ndiyalelwe ukuba ndizinikele eNkosini yamaphakade.’’"
  40,67,"Nguye Owanidalayo ngothuli, emva koko ngeqabaza lembewu yomntu, emva koko ngehlwili elinamathelayo; emva koko Unikhuphela ngaphandle ningabantwana, Aphinde Aniphucule nifikelele ebuntwini, Niphinde nibe ngamaxhego. Ukanti phakathi kwenu kukho abo bathatyathwa bafe phambi (koko) khona ukuze nifikelele kwithuba elithile; mhlawumbi niya kuyisebenzisa ingqiqo"
  40,68,"NguYe Onika ubomi Enze ukufa; Xa Emisela into Usuka Athi kuyo: “Yibakho”, ibekho"
  40,69,Akubaboni na ukuba baphambuke njani na abo baphikisana nemiqondiso ka-Allâh
  40,70,Abo bayiphikayo iNcwadi (i’Kur’ân) noko Sakuthumela abaThunywa beThu baza kwazi
  40,71,Xa amakhamandela ebathandele ezintanyeni zabo namakhonkco; baya kurhuqwa
  40,72,Emanzini abilayo; naseMlilweni baya kuhlohlwa (amadangatya oMlilo eziswini zabo)
  40,73,"Kuze kuthiwe kubo: “Baphi na abo nanidla ngokubayamanisa njengamahlulelane (kuAllâh)"
  40,74,"bengengo-Allâh?’’ Baya kuthi bona: “Basishiyile: gxebe, asizanga sinqule nto thina ngaphambili,” Ubalahlekisa ngolo hlobo ke uAllâh abangakholwayo"
  40,75,"(Iingelosi ziya kuthi): “Oko kwaba ngenxa yokuba nina nanizikhukhumalisa emhlabeni ngokungekho lungelweni yaye naniziphethe ngolunya"
  40,76,"NgenanikeemasangweniesiHogonihlaleaphongonaphakade, hayi ukungcola kwendawo yokuhlala izikhukhumali!”"
  40,77,"Ngoko ke wena (Muhammad) yiba nomonde; inene isithembiso sika-Allâh siyinyaniso. Enokuba Singakubonisa inxalenye yoko Sibathembise kona okanye Sikuthabathe wena ngokufa, kukuThi apho baza kubuyiselwa khona"
  40,78,"Ke kaloku Sanithumela abaThunywa ngaphambi kwenu. Phakathi kwabo kukho abo (iimbali zabo) sele Sikubalisele ngazo, kuze phakathi kwabo kubekho abo (iimbali zabo) Singakubaliselanga ngazo. Kananjalo yayingekokwakhe nawuphi na uMthunywa ukuba eze nomqondiso (okanye iVesi) ngaphandle kwemvume ka-Allâh. Ngoko ke xa umyalelo ka-Allâh ufika uya kufezekiswa ngenyaniso baze abaqambi bobuxoki balahlekelwe"
  40,79,"NguAllâh Owanenzela izilwanyana ezidla ingca eniziqabelayo, ukanti ezinye zazo niyazidla"
  40,80,"Ukanti kwalapho kuzo nineenzuzo (ezizezinye) kanti kwalapho kuzo nifezekisa iimfuno ezisezifubeni5 zenu, ukanti zona neenqanawa ziyanithwala"
  40,81,Ke kaloku Yena Unibonise imiqondiso yaKhe ngoko ke yiyiphi le miqondiso ka-Allâh niyiphikayo
  40,82,"Kanti abakahamba-hambi na ehlabathini babone ukuba sabanjani na isiphelo sabo babandulelayo? babebaninzi ngakumbi kunabo, benamandla nomfaneleko ngakumbi kunabo ehlabathini, kodwa azanga bancedakale koko bakusebenzelayo"
  40,83,"Kananjalo ukufika kwabaThunywa babo kubo nobungqina obucacileyo, (basuka) bagutyungelwa koko babekugculela"
  40,84,"Ke kaloku bakubona isohlwayo seThu, bathi: “Sikholwa kuAllâhYedwathina,asikholwakokobesikadesikwayamanisa naYe.”"
  40,85,"Kodwa aluzanga ukholo lwabo lubancede (nto), ukubonana kwabo nesohlwayo seThu. (Sona) yindlela eyamiselwayo ka-Allâh Aqubisana ngayo nezicaka zaKhe. Apho ke abangakholwayo balahlekelwa (yinto yonke)"
  41,1,Hâ Mîm
  41,2,"(Esi siTyhilelo) sivela (kuAllâh), uSolubabalo, uSozinceba"
  41,3,"INcwadi eVesi zayo zichazwe ngengcombolo, i’Kur’ân yesiArabhu kubantu abanolwazi"
  41,4,"Ingumniki weendaba ezivuyisayo ikwangumlumkisi; kodwa abaninzi kubo bayatshikila, ngoko ke abeva"
  41,5,"Kananjalo bathi: “Iintliziyo zethu ziphantsi kwezigqubuthelo malunga noko usimemela kuko, yaye ezindlebeni zethu kukho ubuthulu, kunjalo nje phakathi kwethu nani kukho umsantsa, ngoko ke sebenza wena nathi siyasebenza.”"
  41,6,"Yithi (Muhammad): “Mna ndingumntu njengani ekutyhilwe kuye okokuba uThixo wenu nguThixo oMnye; ngoko ke thabathani iNdlela ethe Ngqo eya kuYe, nicele itarhu kuYe. ‘’Kananjalo yeha kwabo bayamanisa abanye kuAllâh"
  41,7,"Abo banganikeliyo ngeZakâh, bona kuBomi belizayo abakholwa"
  41,8,"Inene bona abo bakholwayo, benze izenzo ezilungileyo okwabo ngumvuzo ongenakuphazamiseka"